com.amazonaws.services.transcribe

Interface AmazonTranscribeAsync

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AmazonTranscribe
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmazonTranscribeAsyncClient

    public interface AmazonTranscribeAsync
extends AmazonTranscribe
    Interface for accessing Amazon Transcribe asynchronously.

    Operations and objects for transcribing speech to text.
